    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to see that \"value\" when i'm just waiting for a decline that's already happening. it feels like i've lost all my agency over my own life. everything is just happening TO me now, whether it's the sickness or the aging. i wish i could just... decide when enough is enough, instead of just letting it happen.",
